<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>qwmy ʿrws ạlrb</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- qūmī ʿarūsa ạlrãbĩ lạa
 tuʿ̊yī mina ạlsũh̊di
 laki ʿarīsuⁿ fī ạl̊ʿulạ
 wah̊wa rajā ạl̊maj̊di

[V2]
 2- tuq̊ti lahu fī gẖur̊baẗiⁿ
 fī ʿālami ạl̊haẘli
 ḥaẙtẖu ạl̊jihādu wāl̊ʿanā
 wawaḥ̊sẖaẗu ạllãẙli

[V3]
 3- faqad̊ tanāhay̱ ạllãẙlu
 wālṣũb̊ḥu danā jidãạ
 wālrãbũ ậtiⁿ mus̊riʿaⁿạ
 līun̊jiza ạl̊waʿ̊dạ

[V4]
 4- ại̹dẖ̊ qal̊buhu ạl̊musẖ̊tāqu lạ
 yaḥ̊tamilu ạltãạ̊̉kẖīr̊
 faʿājilạaⁿ yā̊̉kẖudẖuki
 limaj̊dihi ạl̊munīr̊

[V5]
 5- wayā̊̉kẖudẖu ạl̊mul̊ka ạlãdẖī
 lahu ʿalay̱ ạl̊jamīʿ̊
 wasatarāhu ạlạảr̊ḍu fī
 kur̊sīĩhi ạlrãfīʿ̊

[V6]
 6- wasatarāki maʿahu
 fī ạl̊maj̊di wāl̊mul̊ki
 baʿ̊da ạn̊qiḍā ạl̊gẖur̊baẗi
 wālậlạami wālḍãn̊ki

[V7]
 7- lima ạlạảsay̱ baʿ̊du ại̹dẖaⁿạ
 surĩy walạ tab̊kī
 fahā laki ạlrãbũ wahā
 ạl̊kulũ kadẖā laki</lyrics>
<author>ạ̹ylyạ zkryạ ʿwḍ ạllh</author>
<hymn_number>5259</hymn_number>
</song>